msgid "If for any reason the system does not continue to boot, the bootstrap can be interrupted by pressing <keycap>space</keycap> at the 10-seconds warning. The loader variable <literal>vinum.autostart</literal> can be examined by typing <command>show</command> and manipulated using <command>set</command> or <command>unset</command>."
